## Implementation Notes

The implementation follows the official Vercel Speed Insights documentation for Next.js App Router:
- Fetched latest instructions from https://vercel.com/docs/speed-insights/quickstart
- Used the framework-specific implementation for Next.js App Router (v13.5+)
- Component placed at the end of the `<body>` tag as recommended
- No additional configuration required

## Next Steps for Deployment

To enable Speed Insights on Vercel:
1. Deploy this project to Vercel
2. Navigate to your project in the Vercel dashboard
3. Select "Speed Insights" from the sidebar
4. Click "Enable" to activate Speed Insights for your project

Once enabled and deployed, the tracking script will automatically inject, and performance metrics will begin appearing in the Speed Insights dashboard after users visit your site.

